{"type": "article", "id": 8678, "title": "Slit 系列桌子", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-20T07:29:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235315vcxQw6rlo7uMIkXA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t丹麦家居品牌 Hay 近来推出了一款名为 “Slit” 的桌子系列，这些看起来像是折纸的桌子实际上是金属材料，有圆形，矩形，多边形等不同的几何形状，而在色彩，设计师的选择除了基本的黑白灰，还有各种粉嫩的配色。桌子名字 “Slit” 来源自每个桌子中间都有一条窄窄的缝隙——小小的细节让桌子更加靠近折纸的设计风格。<a href=\"http://hauslondon.com/products/slit-table-by-hay\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235314r853pu04DwHo2j7O.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235314AlPVyrmDOUx6Gj5Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.60925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052353145UOa64ef9RGBMrgz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.63703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235315cOoWj3TkyVQ9sP1r.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}